{"tid":580082,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[人生交叉點］有個有錢佬話要包養我，如何是好","createTime":"2018-03-04T07:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T11:15:57.000Z","uid":93485,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a1125ea1b59ef43c502f2b00595b75e3ee5e9e","tid":580082,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"利申：真絲<br />\n一個星期前同班FD出黎吃飯，有個FD就帶左個有錢佬出黎，果晚已經FEEL到佢係咁望鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後果日返到屋企，有個唔識既人add鳩我whatsapp say hi, 我已經feel到係佢。<br />\n<br />\n唉，我老豆呢一年衰爛賭，差落70萬銀行財仔數，20萬街數，又唔知邊條友同個有錢佬爆響口，俾佢知道我屋企欠債，結果佢提出幫我還哂90萬，做佢女朋友一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女朋友......即係佢係1...要屌我個閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都未比男朋友屌過個閪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉，宜家心情真係好複雜，條有錢佬又話可以唔公開，但一諗起幫佢含撚同比佢屌閪就好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫你地班仆街仔計埋數喇。<br />\n90萬一年，每月7.5萬，當一個月屌8次，差唔多1萬1次，係幾吸引既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但重點重點係...佢有愛滋我咪玩撚完？？？<br />\n咁我咪做左雞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做雞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻豬值千金"},{"pid":"bfaa7e96d77afbc086b07efa9bc8f741ef277503","tid":580082,"uid":23198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"你咪撚煩啦"},{"pid":"c00180223132d079d7799b566a0b613129f12779","tid":580082,"uid":174150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9a1125ea1b59ef43c502f2b00595b75e3ee5e9e","tid":580082,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor